label lb_intro_07_mc_call_s_0:
    show sc apartm a06
    s"I‚Äôve spent so much time trying to find you on various social media pages, through contacts at the Navy base that Gerald worked at, and even your old school!"
    jump lb_intro_07_mc_call_s_0b

label lb_intro_07_mc_call_s_0b:
    show sc apartm a07
    mc"So you‚Äôve kind of been cyber stalking me all this time?"
    s"Haha, kind of yeah."
    s"I was at my wits end trying to locate your whereabouts to even just get a number to call you at."
    show sc apartm a06
    s"As I said it wasn‚Äôt easy, mainly due to you and Gerald having such a common surname."
    mc"Oh yeah, that would‚Äôve made things difficult for sure!"
    show sc apartm a07
    mc"It may as well have been Smith or Brown, hey?"
    show sc apartm a06
    s"Yeah, exactly! It wasn‚Äôt until a friend of mine started working at a big name mobile phone company..."
    s"That I asked her if she could search for your contact details when I went to visit her."
    s"Your date of birth was a match to the file she pulled up, and it was just by dumb luck that we both use the same service provider too!"
    show sc apartm a09
    mc"I see‚Ä¶ But isn‚Äôt that kind of illegal for her to check for my personal information like that?"
    show sc apartm a06
    s"Well I don‚Äôt know, you tell me mister high school pre-law club man?"
    show sc apartm a09
    mc"I see that you checked into my high school history too!"
    s"Yeah, and it‚Äôs very interesting indeed [y_name]. A little nerdy, but cute as heck."
    show sc apartm a07
    mc"Thanks. I‚Äôm beside myself right now‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs so great to hear from you [s_name]."
    show sc apartm a09
    mc"I just wish you had found me sooner."
    show sc apartm a06
    s"Yeah I know. But my mother, you remember Ashley?"
    show sc apartm a07
    mc"Hehe, how could I forget!"
    show sc apartm a06
    jump lb_intro_07_mc_call_s_1

label lb_intro_07_mc_call_s_1:
    s"Well once we moved back home, she forced me to cut all ties off from you and your Dad."

label lb_intro_07_mc_call_s_2:
    s"I felt so terrible that I couldn‚Äôt even contact you to let you know, and I was worried that you thought I was purposely avoiding you."
    s"I just hope after all this time that you can forgive me."
    show sc apartm a09
