label lb_intro_13_mc_bed:
    scene sc introhotel h51
    with dissolve
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶)"
    show sc introhotel h60
    mc"(It's so nice to be able to finally get some rest after a long day. I gotta say, it feels a little strange to have a bed all to myself for a change.)"
