    mc"(Because before I know it, I‚Äôll be back home where my life is a lot more serious, and I could be doing sixty hour working weeks again.)"
    mc"(I wonder how Nicole is doing, all alone, without me in our bed tonight?)"
    mc"(I‚Äôd like to think that being apart for the next three months will be good for our relationship, and we will realise just how much we‚Äôve really missed each other.)"
    mc"(Well, that‚Äôs what I‚Äôm hoping‚Ä¶)"
    # (Friend pops her head to see if the MC is awake. We only see her head, not what she‚Äôs wearing just yet)"
