    show sc day1cafe c27
    s"Thank you so much for coming and meeting with us this afternoon. We‚Äôll be in touch with you both soon hopefully."
    show sc day1cafe c08
    ivy"Do you have anything you want to ask either me or my sister while you have our attention [y_name]?"
    # [Their necklaces / Tell the difference / Not really]"
