label lb_day1_mc_meets_roshi:
    scene sc day1roshi r01
    with dissolve
    s"Mister Roshi, are you down there?"
    ro"Ahh yes, I‚Äôm here Miss [s_name]."
    show sc day1roshi r02
    s"Hey there. I‚Äôd like to introduce you to someone. This is [y_name]."
    show sc day1roshi r08
    jump lb_day1_mc_meets_roshi_1

label lb_day1_mc_meets_roshi_1:
    s"He‚Äôs a good friend of mine, and he‚Äôs come to help us with the hotel."

label lb_day1_mc_meets_roshi_2:
    show sc day1roshi r11
    mc"Nice to meet you Mister Roshi."
    ro"Hai. And you [y_name]. So what brings young man here?"
    show sc day1roshi r10
    mc"[s_name] actually. I‚Äôm here to help her bring the hotel back up to scratch and to bring some more business in for her."
    show sc day1roshi r11
    ro"Ahh yes, hotel have many problems."
    ro"Not completely unfixable, but we could do with more help, more hands available."
    show sc day1roshi r10
    mc"It sounds like we may have some good people willing to help out already."
    mc"And I myself am pretty good with numbers, organising paperwork and I consider myself a bit of a handy man."
    show sc day1roshi r07
    s"Mister Roshi specialises in being a mister fix-it too."
    show sc day1roshi r08
    s"He‚Äôs done some amazing work with the plumbing and making sure all the locks on the doors function correctly."
    show sc day1roshi r12
    ro"Hai, this is true."
    show sc day1roshi r10
    mc"So what are the main things that are in need of repair?"
    show sc day1roshi r09
    ro"Rooms need new coat of paint, furniture need repairs or replacing. The bed sheets and curtains could do with updating as well."
    show sc day1roshi r05
    s"And the lighthouse lamp needs to be replaced, but that‚Äôs a really expensive repair."
    show sc day1roshi r06
    mc"Okay, well let‚Äôs not make that a priority for now."
    show sc day1roshi r10
    mc"As I said to [s_name], I‚Äôm going to go through the hotel expenses for the past quarter, maybe the past twelve months, and to see where we can cut back in a few areas."
    mc"That way we might be able to put the money into fixing some of the things you just listed Mister Roshi."
    mc"Nobody is going to want to stay here or leave the hotel positive reviews if you have busted pieces of furniture or rooms that haven‚Äôt been updated with a coat of paint in a long time."
    show sc day1roshi r11
    ro"I have quite a number of tins of paint, brushes, rollers and painting equipment in storage house out back."
    ro"We could use those to maybe paint west wing of hotel."
    mc"Okay, that‚Äôs a start. So if we can work on getting those rooms painted by the end of the week, that would be handy."
    show sc day1roshi r10
    mc"And if we have any guests who book in from the weekend onward, then we could book them into the newly painted rooms."
    mc"We would need a day or two to properly air out the paint smell before people start occupying them."
    show sc day1roshi r06
    s"What about the furniture and the curtains?"
    mc"For now, you should go through what we should keep and what needs to be replaced."
    mc"Again, all the best stuff could be used for the west wing of the hotel."
    mc"If you can manage to get some decent business, then we can start working on the east wing and what we need to fix over there."
    show sc day1roshi r09
    ro"We are going to need some more staff members young man. You can‚Äôt run business with just three people, especially if one of them is old man like me."
    mc"Yes of course. [s_name] and I are still working on that."
    show sc day1roshi r10
    mc"Is there anything else I should know about this place that I haven‚Äôt been told as yet?"
    show sc day1roshi r12
    ro"Yes, girls only."
    show sc day1roshi r06
    mc"I‚Äôm sorry? What does that mean exactly?"
    show sc day1roshi r08
    s"What Mister Roshi is trying to say is that the hotel only caters for females."
    show sc day1roshi r06
    mc"Really? Why is that?"
    mc"(And why didn‚Äôt [s_name] tell me this already??)"
    show sc day1roshi r05
    s"It‚Äôs just the way it‚Äôs always been since the first owners, two females, established the hotel in the nineteen hundreds."
    show sc day1roshi r06
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ That seems a tad unusual. Maybe even a bit sexist.)"
    mc"(But if those rules have been put in place for over a hundred years, then there‚Äôs no reason to change them now.)"
    mc"All right, I‚Äôm going to have a look in the main office and go through a few things."
    mc"Then I‚Äôll have a good look around the hotel and will make up a list of things that need to be attended to right away. "
    mc"Start rounding up the paint supplies, and we‚Äôll get to working on these rooms this afternoon if you‚Äôre both up for it?"
    show sc day1roshi r07
    s"Yep, we‚Äôll be ready to go!"
    show sc day1roshi r08
    mc"Great. Once you‚Äôve got all the stuff ready, come and find me [s_name]."
    s"Sure thing."
    show sc day1roshi r10
    mc"Mister Roshi, great to meet you."
    show sc day1roshi r11
    ro"As am I young man. You‚Äôre in for a few hard weeks, maybe months."
    mc"(If I decide to stick around that is‚Ä¶)"
    mc"I don‚Äôt doubt that. Okay, I‚Äôll chat to you both a little later on."
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)




label lb_day1_gerald_call:
    scene sc day1office o17
    with dissolve
    mc"(Damn‚Ä¶ There are so many things here that [s_name] doesn‚Äôt need to spend money on.)"
    show sc day1office o18
    mc"(If I cut down the cost of their electricity, and these friends of hers are happy to work for next to nothing, for a few weeks at least...)"
    mc"(Then we can potentially put that money towards some of the repairs and online promotion.)"
    mc"(Maybe even pay for our own advertisement in and around town‚Ä¶)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Sound_Effect_-_Cell_phone_vibration.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    show sc day1office o01
