            s"You would?"
            mc"Yeah, of course I would."
            jump lb_day1_mc_answer_3

            label lb_day1_mc_answer_3:
            mc"I mean, I know we haven‚Äôt seen each other in a long time, but you‚Äôre still an important person in my life, my childhood especially."

            label lb_day1_mc_answer_4:
