            show sc day2cdate1 c53
            mc"I‚Äôm so sorry [c_name]. That was entirely my fault."
            # (I think my knees broke my fall rather than [c_name].)"
            show sc day2cdate1 c54
            c"No uh‚Ä¶ I think I was a little clumsy and didn‚Äôt get a proper grip of your hands."
            show sc day2cdate1 c53
            mc"Let‚Äôs just say we‚Äôre equally to blame here."
            show sc day2cdate1 c54
            c"Um‚Ä¶ Do you mind getting off me?"
            mc"Oh right, yes, of course. Sorry."
            mc"(Way to go there [y_name]. I‚Äôm sure [c_name] won‚Äôt forget this embarrassing moment between us any time soon‚Ä¶)"
            # (MC gets up, offers his hands again)"


    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
