    mc"Oh, what makes you think there‚Äôs something wrong between us?"
    show sc day2cdate1 c40
    c"Well, I picked up on a few tell-tale signs."
    c"I mean, after what happened between [s_name] and her Mom, it must have been hard for you to be right in the middle of that."
    c"And there‚Äôs also the fact you came to meet me alone, rather than with [s_name]."
    show sc day2cdate1 c38
