        mc"(I still have my trust issues with her, but for the sake of the hotel and the fact that I still have a job to do here, we need to come to a peaceful resolution that works for both of us.)"
        mc"(Even if it means that [s_name] and I still need to keep a distance from each other after the work day has ended‚Ä¶)"
