label lb_day2_ashleydate1_5:
    ash"Don‚Äôt give up on [s_name]."

label lb_day2_ashleydate1_6:
    ash"She needs you, just as much as you need her, otherwise she never would‚Äôve called you, and you never would have agreed to come here, right?"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ She‚Äôs got me there.)"
    mc"Yeah, I guess you‚Äôre right."
    show sc day2ashdate1 a24
    ash"(It‚Äôs so hard to look at [y_name] and to not think of his father.)"
    ash"(Is it possible that he‚Äôs even better looking than when I first met Gerald?)"
    ash"(Ughh! Get a grip Ashley! [y_name] is, how old?)"
    ash"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Old enough, certainly. Shit! I‚Äôm acting like a damn cougar! I better ask him to leave before I do or say something stupid!)"
    show sc day2ashdate1 a19
    ash"Anyway, I don‚Äôt mean to be rude, but I‚Äôm going to have to ask you to leave, as I have somewhere I need to be soon."
    mc"Sure, no problems. Don‚Äôt let me keep you."
