    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    show sc day2ashdate1 a04
    with dissolve
    mc"So uhh, thanks for your time Ashley."
    show sc day2ashdate1 a03
    ash"You‚Äôre welcome. Say‚Ä¶ If you‚Äôre interested, you should come up to where I work in the mountains some time?"
    show sc day2ashdate1 a06
    ash"It‚Äôs quite a sight up there, and I could give you a grand tour of what I‚Äôve been working on for all these years."
