    ash"Plus coffee will be on me!"
    show sc day2ashdate1 a06
    mc"Oh, that would be great! As would the coffee!"
    show sc day2ashdate1 a03
    ash"Haha! Excellent‚Ä¶"
    show sc day2ashdate1 a04
    mc"As I‚Äôll be busy at this hotel with [s_name], I‚Äôll have to find some free time to come up to see you."
    show sc day2ashdate1 a06
    ash"Sure, you just call me whenever it suits."
    mc"I will."
    # (Ashley leans in close to him)"
    ash"And [y_name]‚Ä¶"
