    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day2ashdate1 a03
    ash"Don‚Äôt be a stranger, and remember what I said, keep your options open‚Ä¶"
    show sc day2ashdate1 a06
    mc"Uh, sure thing Ashley. Bye‚Ä¶"
    ash"See ya!"
    # (Ashley closes the door as the MC leaves)"
    # (he stands outside her place, pondering his thoughts)"
    show sc day2ashdate1 a02
    mc"(Okay, now that was strange conversation in parts. It could be just me, but was Ashley flirting with me?)"
