label lb_day2_victoriadate1_2:
    show sc day2vicdate1 v26
    mc"Uhh, what do you mean Victoria?"
    show sc day2vicdate1 v25
    vic"You know what I mean [y_name]. There was obviously some friction between you two when I spoke to you both last."
