    mc"There‚Äôs a lot to tell though."
    mc"Don‚Äôt get me wrong, I‚Äôm really happy to be here in Sunshine Bay, but I‚Äôm learning things about [s_name] and the hotel that I‚Äôve not been happy with."
    show sc day2vicdate1 v25
    vic"So, you‚Äôre going to quit on her?"
