label lb_day2_victoriadate1_4:
    show sc day2vicdate1 v26
    menu:
        "Ask about the burlesque house"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc day2vicdate1 v26
            mc"I‚Äôm just curious Victoria but, can I ask you something about the burlesque house in town?"
            show sc day2vicdate1 v25
            vic"Uh, okay‚Ä¶"
            vic"Now it‚Äôs me that is starting to wonder why you would ask me that kind of question [y_name]?"
            show sc day2vicdate1 v26
            mc"It‚Äôs not how it sounds Victoria."
            mc"It‚Äôs just that I saw this poster yesterday, where some religious group was trying to get this particular establishment shut down."
