            vic"They‚Äôve been trying to get that place closed down for a while now."
            vic"Drinking, gambling, debauchery and other such adult activities that take place in there is something that is heavily frowned upon by the Reverend and his wife."
            vic"They see the burlesque house as a modern day strip club..."
            vic"And the people that are a part of their church or their community group, Faith plus one, want to see it closed down as soon as possible."
            show sc day2vicdate1 v26
