            mc"Do you think that they will succeed?"
            vic"It‚Äôs hard to say right now."
            show sc day2vicdate1 v26
            vic"But I do feel like the reason why these laws have never changed‚Ä¶"
            vic"Is due to people in town who don‚Äôt like the fact that this organisation has an annoying habit of sticking their noses in places where they shouldn‚Äôt."
            vic"Just like the lighthouse, the burlesque house is a big part of Sunshine Bay‚Äôs history, and locals would like to see it continue operating for many years to come."
            mc"Yeah, I can imagine."
            # (Vicky puts a hand over her mouth)"
            show sc day2vicdate1 v28
            vic"Oh my god, I can‚Äôt believe I‚Äôm talking about this kind of thing with you?"
            vic"I‚Äôm so sorry [y_name]."
            show sc day2vicdate1 v26
            mc"No Victoria, it‚Äôs my fault. I was the one who asked."
            mc"But I kind of wish I hadn‚Äôt seen that poster, you know?"
            show sc day2vicdate1 v23
