label lb_day2_victoriadate1_evening:
    if _in_replay:
        if y_name == None:
            $ y_name = "MC"
        else:
            $ y_name = persistent.y_name
        show screen toprightmenu

        play music "music/01/2936-fliegen-by-sascha-ende.mp3"
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day2vicdad v01b","v_rewards_victoria_09")
    scene sc day2vicdad v01
    vic"(Where is that damn dress? The girls won‚Äôt wait outside for me forever.)"
    vic"(Ah, here it is!)"
    # (Victoria pulls a dress out of her closet)"
    vic"(I better put this on before Papi comes home. I could do without seeing him.)"
    # (screen goes blank)"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (Victoria has changed into this dress and heels, and poses in front of a mirror - https://pixhost.to/show/62/139817328_vic_01.jpg)"
    scene sc day2vicdad v02
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day2vicdad v02b","v_rewards_victoria_10")
    vic"(I can‚Äôt believe I left this dress behind when I moved out.)"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    if renpy.loadable("extras.animations") and persistent.v_anim_enabled:
        window hide
        scene wip_02_vic_dress  at tt_top
        pause
        window show
    else:
        show sc day2vicdad v03
    vic"(I really love it.)"
    show sc day2vicdad v04
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day2vicdad v04b","v_rewards_victoria_11")
    vic"(And these heels look fantastic as well.)"
    # (Vicky‚Äôs father Danny enters the room - https://i.pinimg.com/originals/1d/50/a4/1d50a4731fb1268c9aec856eb5b047a4.jpg)"
    da"Victoria, you‚Äôre home!"
    # (Vicky surprised look)"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day2vicdad v05
    vic"Oh, hey Papi. I was just about to leave."
    show sc day2vicdad v07
    da"I see that you‚Äôre all dressed up. You have a date, don‚Äôt you? What‚Äôs his name?"
    show sc day2vicdad v09
    vic"It‚Äôs not what you think Dad. Did you see the car out front?"
    show sc day2vicdad v10
    vic"That‚Äôs my best friend Rosita. We‚Äôre going out for dinner and drinks."
    show sc day2vicdad v06
    da"I sincerely hope you‚Äôre not going to a restaurant that is one of my competitors?"
    show sc day2vicdad v09
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day2vicdad v05b","v_rewards_victoria_12")
    vic"Of course not, I wouldn‚Äôt betray you like that Papi. We‚Äôre going to an Italian restaurant."
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day2vicdad v16
    da"Madre de dios! Que Chinga What!?"
    # (*This means ‚ÄúOh dear lord!‚Äù in English.)"
    show sc day2vicdad v09
    vic"Oh come on Papi! You can‚Äôt expect me to eat the food of our people all the time."
    show sc day2vicdad v07
    da"Of course. Look Victoria, we need to talk?"
    show sc day2vicdad v09
    vic"Okay, but you‚Äôre gonna have to make it quick."
    show sc day2vicdad v06
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day2vicdad v13b","v_rewards_victoria_13")
    da"When are you going to come and work for me at my restaurant? "
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day2vicdad v05
    vic"You know why I can‚Äôt do that Papi. I have my own business."
    show sc day2vicdad v07
    da"But honey, the food truck business is no way to make a living, there‚Äôs no reason for your career in the food industry to be confined to such a small kitchen."
    show sc day2vicdad v09
    vic"With all due respect Papi, I‚Äôm not going over this with you again."
    vic"Besides, I‚Äôm going to be doing even bigger business with a major hotel in town thanks to a couple of people I‚Äôve met."
    show sc day2vicdad v07
    da"What hotel? What business?"
    show sc day2vicdad v10
    vic"Well if you must know, it‚Äôs the hotel up on the hill, next to the lighthouse."
    vic"I went to the same college with the girl who co-runs it and I spent some time showing this guy she knows how to run my business."
    show sc day2vicdad v06
    da"A guy? What guy?"
    show sc day2vicdad v09
    vic"It‚Äôs not what you think Papi."
    show sc day2vicdad v07
    da"You let some guy work alongside you in that food truck?"
    show sc day2vicdad v06
    da"(I think she doesn‚Äôt want to tell me she‚Äôs seeing this man.)"
    show sc day2vicdad v12
    vic"Oh my god Papi! I can‚Äôt believe you?"
    show sc day2vicdad v07
    da"What??"
    show sc day2vicdad v11
    vic"You always get like this whenever I mention guys. And for your information, it‚Äôs not like that at all."
    vic"It‚Äôs strictly business, and I was the one calling the shots."
    show sc day2vicdad v13
    da"Why can't you be more like your brother Miguel?"
    show sc day2vicdad v07
    da"He has a restaurant of his own now after spending a few short years working under me."
    da"All I‚Äôm saying is that you could have the same Victoria."
    show sc day2vicdad v09
    vic"Ughh!! It‚Äôs not what I want Papi! I want my own independence, and I don‚Äôt want anybody‚Äôs help."
    vic"Not yours, not anybody‚Äôs. Why can‚Äôt you understand that?"
    show sc day2vicdad v15
    da"Oh your poor grandmother. She would hate to see you like this Victoria, you know?"
    show sc day2vicdad v11
    vic"(Oh great. Now he‚Äôs trying to guilt-trip me by mentioning my Abuela.)"
    vic"(I can‚Äôt be here any longer, otherwise it will just end up with me and Papi having another one of our huge disagreements.)"
    vic"Look, I gotta go Papi. I‚Äôm sorry."
    show sc day2vicdad v08
    da"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    da"I‚Äôm sorry too. Bye Victoria."
    if _in_replay:
        scene black
        with dissolve
        scene black
        with Pause (2)
    $ persistent.day2_victoriadate1_evening = False
    $ renpy.end_replay()
