label lb_day2_nicole_calls:
    # (SOW) 09 - Nicole calls the MC back when he returns to the lighthouse."
    # - The MC is talking to his Best Friend"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (the MC is about to enter the hotel, he is standing in the courtyard area when his phone goes off)"
    # (Phone ringing - sound effect)"
    scene sc day2nicolecall c01
    with dissolve
    play sound "sound effects/01/00/Cell_Phone_Ring_Sound_Effect.mp3" fadein 1.0
    "(Phone rings)"
    stop sound
    show sc day2nicolecall c04
    mc"Hello?"
    nic"Hey, it‚Äôs me."
    mc"Nicole!"
    nic"Can I just start by saying, how could you forget to call me last night??"
    mc"Honey, I am so sorry."
    mc"It was a long day, and I completely forgot about the time difference and I didn‚Äôt want to wake you."
    nic"Okay, okay, calm down. It‚Äôs fine. Look, I have a few minutes before I have to go back to the office."
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    nic"So just give me the gist of what‚Äôs happening down there?"
    mc"Well, I think I might be okay actually."
    show sc day2nicolecall c04
    mc"[s_name] and I argued last night and again this morning about the business, about the hotel, but I feel like, after much thought, I can take care of it now."
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    nic"Are you sure there‚Äôs nothing that I should be worried about?"
    jump lb_day2_nicole_calls_1

label lb_day2_nicole_calls_1:
    nic"I mean, the last thing I need to hear is you having a falling out with the only person you know in that town."

label lb_day2_nicole_calls_2:
    show sc day2nicolecall c05
    mc"You have nothing to worry about, I‚Äôm confident that I have everything under control."
    mc"I‚Äôve met some pretty awesome people already, and they seem very interested in helping us out."
    nic"That‚Äôs great to hear babe."
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    mc"By the way, did you speak to my Dad?"
    nic"Yeah, he um, he called here yesterday asking for you."
    show sc day2nicolecall c04
    mc"Uh-huh. Look, he called me so I know you told him where I was and why I‚Äôm here."
    mc"I‚Äôm not angry because he was going to find out one way or another."
    mc"All I want to know is, did he say anything to you about me coming here?"
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    nic"No, not much. I mean he wasn‚Äôt happy about it. But I tried to convince your father that you needed to go."
    show sc day2nicolecall c05
    mc"Thanks, Nicky."
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    mc"Aside from that, he didn‚Äôt say anything else, did he?"
    nic"No, he just asked how I was, and that he‚Äôd give me a call if he was in town to see if I‚Äôd meet him for coffee somewhere."
    nic"That‚Äôs pretty much it."
    show sc day2nicolecall c04
    jump lb_day2_nicole_calls_3

label lb_day2_nicole_calls_3:
    mc"He always liked you, you know? Heck, sometimes I feel like he wishes you were his child, instead of me."
    nic"You know that‚Äôs not true [y_name]. Your Dad just wants what‚Äôs best for you."

label lb_day2_nicole_calls_4:
    nic"Did you and your Dad get into an argument?"
    mc"Yeah we did."
    mc"He didn‚Äôt approve of me being here and he thinks that [s_name] tricked me into coming down to Sunshine Bay to work with her."
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    nic"Well what do you think?"
    show sc day2nicolecall c04
    mc"What‚Äôs that supposed to mean?"
    nic"Nothing. All I‚Äôm saying is as long as you don‚Äôt believe that then it doesn‚Äôt matter what your father thinks."
    nic"And if you are so worried that he might be right, then prove him wrong."
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    nic"Prove to your Dad that you‚Äôre there for the right reasons and that you can work with [s_name]."
    show sc day2nicolecall c05
    mc"Yeah, you‚Äôre right. Thanks Nicole, I really needed to hear that."
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    nic"You‚Äôre welcome. God, I miss you so much already. And you‚Äôve only been gone less than two days."
    show sc day2nicolecall c04
    mc"I know, it‚Äôs so hard being away from you. I‚Äôd give anything just to see you right now."
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    nic"Well‚Ä¶ If you‚Äôre online later, perhaps we could organise something, like maybe, a private session on Hype?"
    show sc day2nicolecall c06
    mc"Oh I see, a bit of a one-on-one video chatting, huh?"
    show sc day2nicolecall c05
    nic"I think the teenagers are calling it Hype-sex or something like that."
    mc"Hmm‚Ä¶ You‚Äôd think they could come up with a better name than that!"
    nic"Haha, for sure. Anyway, I‚Äôll have to end this chat I‚Äôm afraid."
    show sc day2nicolecall c05
    mc"Yes, of course."
    show sc day2nicolecall c04
    mc"Thanks Nicky, and again, I‚Äôm sorry about last night."
    show sc day2nicolecall c03
    nic"It‚Äôs okay, just don‚Äôt stand me up again tonight."
    nic"Actually, I‚Äôll call you this time. So make sure you have your phone or a tablet ready when I do so."
    show sc day2nicolecall c06
    mc"I‚Äôm supergluing my tablet to my hands as we speak."
    show sc day2nicolecall c05
    nic"Haha, I‚Äôm sure you are. All right, have fun [y_name]. But not too much fun."
    jump lb_day2_nicole_calls_5

label lb_day2_nicole_calls_5:
    nic"And go and talk to [s_name], please‚Ä¶"

label lb_day2_nicole_calls_6:
    mc"Yes, I promise. Bye Nicole."
    nic"Goodbye babe‚Ä¶"
    # (call ends)"
    show sc day2nicolecall c02
    mc"(Man, Nicole always has good advice. Which probably explains why she‚Äôs a lawyer and I‚Äôm not.)"
    show sc day2nicolecall c01
    mc"(Anyway, I better go and see what [s_name] is up to, and pray that she‚Äôs not still thinking about this morning or last night‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)





label lb_day2_s_not_fight:
    # (SOW) 10 - MC and Friend decide to try to not fight anymore (for now), they both agree to set some ground rules."
    # - The MC is talking to his Best Friend"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (MC enters the hotel, sees friend in the office, her back turned to him)"
    scene sc day2offices s01
    with dissolve
    mc"(Okay, there she is. Just remain calm, and try no to lose your cool.)"
    mc"Hey‚Ä¶"
    # (Friend turns around, and sees the MC. Friend is wearing some overalls, important for the MOW 01 scene)"
    show sc day2offices s02
    s"Hey [y_name]."
    # (Oh my, he caught me by surprise!) All right, I need to let him know how I feel.)"
    mc"Look, [s_name]. I just wanted to say-"
    # (MC gets cut off)"
    show sc day2offices s03
    s"I‚Äôm sorry about this morning [y_name], and for last night too."
    mc"Huh?"
    show sc day2offices s05
    s"And I‚Äôm really sorry for the way I‚Äôve been acting since you arrived."
    s"You didn‚Äôt deserve that, I should have just been honest with you."
    show sc day2offices s03
    s"And I should be more appreciative of the fact that you came all this way, just for me, and I forgot that."
    # (F takes the MC‚Äôs hands, pleading wth her eyes)"
    show sc day2offices s09
    s"Can we start over?"
    show sc day2offices s03
    mc"(I can‚Äôt believe it!)"
    mc"(I‚Äôm usually the one to apologise first whenever me and Nicole have had a huge fight or disagreement.)"
    show sc day2offices s04
    mc"I uhh, yes, I‚Äôd like that very much. And you know what? I‚Äôm sorry too."
    mc"I was out of line with some of the things I said to you and I regret that."
    mc"I can‚Äôt imagine how stressful all of this must be for you, and I should‚Äôve taken the time to at least try to see things from your point of view."
    mc"So for that I also apologise."
    show sc day2offices s06
    s"Apology accepted."
    show sc day2offices s04
    s"And I was thinking that maybe we should set some ground rules..."
    s"So that these minor ‚Äúdisagreements‚Äù that we‚Äôve had don‚Äôt become a bigger problem for us while you‚Äôre staying with me over the summer."
    s"We should have some boundaries that we both accept."
    mc"Yes, I agree. How about for starters, we keep family and any past history out of our conversations from now on?"
    mc"Let‚Äôs make our complete focus be on the present, and what we hope to achieve in the near future."
    mc"What do you say?"
    show sc day2offices s06
    s"Yep, that works for me."
    s"Unless of course things like family somehow contribute, or become important to the business, and in a positive way."
    mc"Oh, sure."
    jump lb_day2_s_not_fight_1

label lb_day2_s_not_fight_1:
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I can‚Äôt see my Dad being of any real use to [s_name] and me.)"

label lb_day2_s_not_fight_2:
    mc"(And it doesn‚Äôt seem like Ashley will want any part of the hotel, now, or in the future.)"
    show sc day2offices s04
    mc"And when we‚Äôre working, we strictly talk about the business, the hotel, and our clients."
    show sc day2offices s06
    s"Yep, I like that."
    show sc day2offices s04
    s"Any other rules you want to include before we continue?"
    mc"None that I can think of, but we can always add to the list as we go."
    show sc day2offices s07
    s"Haha, okay."
    show sc day2offices s04
    s"So there‚Äôs something important that I‚Äôd like to show you, but before I do so, may I ask, where did you run off to this morning?"
    mc"Uhh‚Ä¶ A few places actually‚Ä¶"
    mc"I um, I went to see your cousin [c_name]‚Ä¶"
    show sc day2offices s05
    s"You did? How come?"
    show sc day2offices s04
    mc"For the business of course..."
    mc"I‚Äôd been thinking a lot about our discussion when we first met..."
    mc"And I figure if we want [c_name] to run the front desk and to handle all of our potential clients and customers, then I ought to get to working with her sooner, rather than later."
    show sc day2offices s06
    s"That‚Äôs great [y_name]! So how did this all come about? "
    show sc day2offices s04
    mc"I just called her with the tablet that you let me borrow. I found her contact details in there, and fortunately, she was free this morning to meet up."
    mc"I also walked her back here as she wanted to go for a surf."
    show sc day2offices s06
    s"Of course she did. So what else did you two talk about?"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ Maybe I shouldn‚Äôt mention to [s_name] that I was talking to [c_name] about the argument we had last night and again this morning.)"
    mc"([s_name] may not appreciate me confiding in another person, especially someone like her cousin.)"
    show sc day2offices s04
    mc"We also created a brief plan on how we can work on her self-confidence issues and how to improve her social skills."
    mc"She did very well this morning [s_name], you would‚Äôve been proud of her."
    show sc day2offices s10
    show screen scr_rewards("sc day2offices s10b","v_rewards_s_14")
    s"You‚Äôre incredible [y_name]!"
    s"When you left this morning, I sure wasn‚Äôt expecting you to come back to tell me this."
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc day2offices s06
    mc"Well what can I say? I guess I found some kind of inspiration to get to work when I left here this morning."
    #(F smiles)"
    show sc day2offices s04
    s"So you said you went to a few places, did you visit anyone else?"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I just agreed to not talk about family with her, and I certainly can‚Äôt tell [s_name] that I went to her Mom‚Äôs place.)"
    mc"(Now that we‚Äôve cleared the air, and things are good between us, I don‚Äôt want to ruin things by telling her I spent time with Ashley!)"
    mc"(I can‚Äôt start off this clean slate by lying to [s_name], especially after I accused her of doing the same thing.)"
    mc"I um‚Ä¶ I also went to see the twins, Lily and Ivy."
    show sc day2offices s05
    s"You did? What for? Did they call to confirm that they want to work with us?"
    show sc day2offices s04
    mc"Lily, whom I mainly spoke to didn‚Äôt say those words exactly."
    mc"But the good news is that they want to see both of us again. I think they want to get an idea of what the events hall here looks like."
    show sc day2offices s07
    s"That‚Äôs awesome [y_name]! I better make sure that it‚Äôs clean and tidy before their arrival."
    show sc day2offices s04
    s"So how did this all come about?"
    mc"I uhh‚Ä¶ Well ever since you introduced me to Ivy and Lily, I just felt the need to see them again."
    s"And what else did you two talk about?"
    mc"The business of course."
    mc"Even though it was evident that they‚Äôre pretty flat out with work, they‚Äôve managed to set aside some time for us tomorrow."
    mc"They‚Äôre looking to go through some more ideas and specific plans for the hotel."
    show sc day2offices s06
    s"That‚Äôs so great [y_name]. I‚Äôm speechless right now at what you‚Äôve already done to help me out."
    mc"Ahh, it was nothing."
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I wonder if I should pass that ‚Äúmessage‚Äù onto [s_name] that the twins asked me to?)"
    #[Don‚Äôt / Pass the message]"
    menu:
        "Don‚Äôt":
            mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I feel kind of weird for even thinking about kissing [s_name], even if it‚Äôs on the cheek.)"
            mc"(Something feels very off about this, like it‚Äôs a practical joke that‚Äôs being played on me or something.)"
        "Pass the message"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc day2offices s04
            mc"Oh, and both of the twins asked me to give this to you‚Ä¶"
            #(MC leans in and kisses f on the cheek, which she really likes) +1 FRIEND POINT"
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,1,s_name)
            play sound "sound effects/01/02/Male_kissing_girl_on_the_cheek.mp3" fadein 1.0
            show sc day2offices s11
            mc"Mwah!"
            stop sound
            show sc day2offices s07
            s"Haha, really?"
            show sc day2offices s06
            mc"Uh, yeah. Does that mean anything to you?"
            show sc day2offices s07
            s"Haha, it sure does."
            mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I‚Äôm obviously missing something here. Perhaps it‚Äôs an inside joke between [s_name] and the twins.)"
            #(scene continues)"
    show sc day2offices s04
    mc"And I also found some time to visit Victoria this morning."
    s"You did, really? Did she call to confirm that she wants to work with us?"
    mc"Vicky didn‚Äôt say those words exactly, but the good news is that she‚Äôs agreed to come and see us both tomorrow as well."
    mc"I think she wants to get a better idea of the layout of the kitchen and the dining room area for the guests."
    show sc day2offices s08
    s"(Wait, did he just call her Vicky? I thought she hated when people called her that. Hmm‚Ä¶ Strange.)"
    show sc day2offices s06
    s"That‚Äôs great [y_name]! So I take it you called her on the tablet as well?"
    mc"Yeah I did."
    mc"She said she was really busy when I called her, so I arrived at her food truck when it was a quieter period for her."
    s"I see. And what else did you two discuss?"
    show sc day2offices s04
    mc"Mainly details about her business."
    mc"I figured that if we‚Äôre going to hire her services, then I should at least take some time to learn what she does every day at her food truck."
    mc"She was kind enough to teach me how to make the perfect taco."
    show sc day2offices s07
    s"Oh my god, she did?"
    show sc day2offices s06
    mc"Haha, yeah."
    mc"I still have quite a lot to learn about the way she runs her business, and the inside of those food trucks are quite cramped for two people!"
    mc"Not to mention how hot and sweaty it gets in there."
    s"So it sounds like you‚Äôve convinced Victoria to be our main food supplier?"
    mc"Almost. It all depends on how tomorrow goes with her. But she seems very interested now."
    show sc day2offices s07
    s"I don‚Äôt know what to say [y_name]. I am truly in awe of you right now."
    show sc day2offices s10
    s"Thank you for doing all this, I‚Äôm at a loss for words."
    mc"Well, we‚Äôre a team, aren‚Äôt we?"
    show sc day2offices s07
    s"Yeah, we are."
    show sc day2offices s08
    mc"So, you said that there was something important that you wanted to show me?"
    show sc day2offices s07
    s"Oh, yes I do! Right this way [y_name]. I have a little surprise of my own‚Ä¶ "
    # (F guides the MC out of the office and to the next room)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)


















label lb_day2_nicole_hang_out:
    # (SOW) 11 - Nicole decides to hang out with someone after work"
    # - The MC is talking to his Best Friend"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (scene starts with Nicole sitting in a bar by herself, thinking about the MC)"
    scene sc day2geonicole n01
    with dissolve
    play sound "sound effects/02/01/Busy_Bar_Ambiance_Noise.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    nic"(I really hope I haven‚Äôt made a mistake by letting [y_name] go down to Sunshine Bay for the summer.)"
    # (Georgina enters the bar, stands next to Nicole)"
    show sc day2geonicole n03
    "Hey Nicky, sorry I‚Äôm late."
    show sc day2geonicole n04
    nic"That‚Äôs okay, I just arrived here myself."
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"Have you ordered anything yet?"
    show sc day2geonicole n07
    nic"No, not yet. I thought I‚Äôd get myself a drink before you arrived."
    show sc day2geonicole n12
    geo"Haha, I might join you for one then."
    show sc day2geonicole n05
    nic"How are things going? I mean professionally."
    show sc day2geonicole n12
    geo"I‚Äôm doing really well!"
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"My manager‚Äôs been able to line up so many modelling jobs for me of late..."
    geo"And it feels like a miracle that I even have the time to come and visit my little sister!"
    show sc day2geonicole n08
    nic"Well I really do appreciate it Gigi."
    show sc day2geonicole n07
    nic"So, do you still have the same feelings and attractions for this guy? Your manager?"
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    menu:
        "Georgina appears resigned":
            show sc day2geonicole n10
            geo"I still like him and care about him a lot. But he just never felt the same way. And I‚Äôm okay with that."
            geo"To be honest, the longer we worked together, the less I thought that we would ever become something more."
            show sc day2geonicole n13
            geo"But the main thing is we‚Äôre still friends, we‚Äôre still close, and he‚Äôs with someone who he was always destined to be with."
            show sc day2geonicole n05
            nic"You‚Äôre being real mature about this sis. Good for you!"
        "Georgina appears happy"(wt="Best choice"):
            $ v_georgina_threesome = True
            show sc day2geonicole n13
            geo"Well actually, I‚Äôm happy to tell you that we‚Äôre currently seeing each other now, officially!"
            show sc day2geonicole n08
            nic"Oh my god, really? When did this happen? Are you happy?"
            show sc day2geonicole n13
            geo"It happened a while ago now, and yes, I am profoundly happy sis."
            geo"For the longest time, I never thought anything would ever happen between us..."
            geo"And despite some initial obstacles, we‚Äôve been able to forge a special relationship that satisfies us both."
            show sc day2geonicole n05
            nic"Oh, okay. Well the main thing is that you‚Äôre happy."
            show sc day2geonicole n12
            geo"Oh, I definitely am!"
            show sc day2geonicole n07
            nic"(Hmm‚Ä¶ It sounds like there‚Äôs a lot more to this relationship with her manager than she‚Äôs letting on.)"
            nic"(Perhaps Gigi will tell me the whole story about how it eventuated some other time.)"










    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"Anyway, enough about me. How are you? How‚Äôs [y_name]?"
    show sc day2geonicole n10
    geo"I figure that something must be wrong if you‚Äôve asked me to come and see you."
    show sc day2geonicole n09
    nic"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    nic"I‚Äôm doing all right I guess. I just spoke to [y_name] a couple of hours ago, he seems to be fine, but‚Ä¶"
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"But what Nicky?"
    show sc day2geonicole n09
    nic"He‚Äôs all the way down there in Sunshine Bay, he has the beach and the sun, while I‚Äôm stuck here with this shitty weather, with nowhere to go and no one to hang out with."
    show sc day2geonicole n10
    geo"Ughh, I don‚Äôt know how you both managed to live here for so long. Every time I come here it‚Äôs either raining or the weather is overcast."
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"Why don‚Äôt you move back closer to me? It wouldn‚Äôt be that big of a move for you and [y_name]."
    show sc day2geonicole n06
    nic"You know why we can‚Äôt do that Gigi."
    nic"This city has all the best law firms, and I can‚Äôt just up and leave my job. Plus we still have our mortgage to pay off."
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"Hmm‚Ä¶ I suppose I can understand that."
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"Say, why don‚Äôt you leave work early on Friday and come with me for some afternoon drinks?"
    geo"My manager has booked me a photoshoot here in the city, and I should be done by four o‚Äôclock."
    geo"I think you‚Äôd really enjoy the place where myself and some of the crew at the studio are thinking of going once we‚Äôre done."
    geo"And being around some nice friendly people would help you to take your mind off of [y_name]."
    show sc day2geonicole n06
    nic"Hmm.. I don‚Äôt know. Can I get back to you on that?"
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"Sure sis."
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"So tell me, honestly, what is it that you‚Äôre really worried about?"
    show sc day2geonicole n09
    nic"I don‚Äôt know. I guess, that maybe [y_name] will meet someone else when he‚Äôs down there."
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"Really? Well, who is he staying with?"
    show sc day2geonicole n07
    jump lb_day2_nicole_hang_out_1

label lb_day2_nicole_hang_out_1:
    nic"He‚Äôs staying with a childhood friend of his, [s_name], for the summer. He‚Äôs there to help her with some hotel that she runs in town."
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"Is she attractive?"
    show sc day2geonicole n06
    nic"I‚Äôve only seen pictures of her, but yeah, she seems quite pretty. Wait, you‚Äôre not suggesting?"
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"Well‚Ä¶ How well do you know this girl?"
    show sc day2geonicole n07
    nic"I don‚Äôt know anything about her, except that her mother was dating [y_name]‚Äôs father for a few years and they all lived under the same roof when he was a kid."
    show sc day2geonicole n10
    geo"Hmm‚Ä¶ What if they‚Ä¶?"
    # (Georgina gives a concerned look)"
    show sc day2geonicole n06
    nic"No, [y_name] wouldn‚Äôt, I‚Äôm almost certain of it. Besides, he said that she‚Äôs like a sister to him."

label lb_day2_nicole_hang_out_2:
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"If you say so. But is [s_name] the only person that he knows in Sunshine Bay?"
    show sc day2geonicole n07
    nic"I‚Äôm not sure if she still lives there, but, the only other person he would know is [s_name]‚Äôs mother."
    nic"I don't recall her name."
    nic"[y_name] did mention during our talk that he‚Äôd already met a few interesting people, and he‚Äôs been there for less than two days."
    nic"And I can‚Äôt be angry at him for doing this because I was the one who suggested that it was a good idea to get to know some of the locals while he‚Äôs there in town."
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"I feel like you‚Äôre getting your panties in a bunch over very little Nicky."
    show sc day2geonicole n09
    nic"Well what do you suggest that I do sis? Just sit here for three months with my thumb up my butt?!"
    show sc day2geonicole n12
    geo"Haha, no, of course not."
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"If you think he‚Äôs down there having a good time with [s_name] and some new people, then what‚Äôs stopping you from doing the same?"
    geo"I mean if it were me, I‚Äôd take the time to spend it with my family or friends."
    show sc day2geonicole n06
    nic"Well, Mom and Dad live several hours away as you know, so I can‚Äôt go and visit them."
    nic"And the only other person that‚Äôs even remotely close to who I‚Äôd call family and that lives nearby is [y_name]‚Äôs father Gerald."
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"Well there‚Äôs another option. But I also think that you should take advantage of this unique situation."
    show sc day2geonicole n07
    nic"Huh? What do you mean sis?"
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"When are you going to talk to [y_name] again?"
    show sc day2geonicole n07
    nic"Tonight, before I go to bed."
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"Well here‚Äôs a perfect chance for you to show [y_name] how much you miss him, and to find out just how much he misses you."
    geo"Have you discussed the idea of teasing each other during video phone chatting?"
    show sc day2geonicole n07
    nic"We did, briefly. But I intended to just do some dirty talk and maybe light teasing."
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"I‚Äôd suggest that you take it up a few notches Nicky."
    geo"You know what I once did with my old boss, who is now my current manager, when we used to work together at the office?"
    geo"I sent him some pictures of myself wearing sexy lingerie, and asked him his opinion of them."
    geo"He was pretty taken aback, mainly because he wasn‚Äôt expecting it."
    show sc day2geonicole n06
    nic"Wow, that was pretty risqu√© of you Georgina."
    show sc day2geonicole n12
    geo"Well, I had to get his attention somehow."
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"And if you‚Äôre not comfortable doing this on camera with [y_name], then you could always get yourself a dildo at the local adult store that‚Äôs the same size, shape, and colour of your boyfriend‚Äôs co-"
    # (Nicky cuts her off)"
    show sc day2geonicole n09
    nic"Okay, okay, I get it."
    # (Nicky bemused, but then lost in thought)"
    show sc day2geonicole n11
    geo"Anyway, all I‚Äôm saying is that three months is a long time to be apart from someone you love, and it can be like torture for some."
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"So you have to make the most of those times when you do talk or when you‚Äôre at home, wishing he was there."
    show sc day2geonicole n09
    nic"(Hmm‚Ä¶ It already feels like torture, even though I‚Äôve tried to downplay it.)"
    nic"I‚Äôll think about it Georgina. Thanks for your advice."
    show sc day2geonicole n12
    geo"Anything for my little sis."
    show sc day2geonicole n13
    geo"Now come on, let‚Äôs order something to eat. I‚Äôm starving!"
    show sc day2geonicole n08
    nic"Haha, sounds good."
    # (screen goes blank)"
