    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    mc"I‚Äôm sure."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y32
    mc"(She looks rather young, like she‚Äôs still in high school!)"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y14
    ro"Oooh‚Ä¶"
    # (Mister Roshi puts a hand to his forehead, feeling light-headed)"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y33
    yuki"Are you feeling okay father?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y14
    ro"I‚Äôm rather tired. Back quite sore from working."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y21
    mc"Maybe you should go and see a doctor?"
    ro"I‚Äôm at an age when my back goes out more than I do young man. I just need rest."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y33
    yuki"Let me walk you back to your room father."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y10
    s"No, allow me to Yuki. I‚Äôll take your Dad so he can have some rest, while you and [y_name] get to know each other."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y31
    yuki"Okay, sounds good. And thanks."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y10
    s"No problem at all."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y32
    yuki"Bye father."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y16
    ro"You show junior here everything I have taught you, my student."
    mc"(Junior?)"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y32
    yuki"Haha, I will."
    # (F walks MR out of the room)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (screen goes blank)"
    # (MOW) 03 - MC and Yuki get some time alone and we learn more about her and her abilities."
    # - The MC is talking to his Best Friend"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (Yuki stares at the door as friend leaves with her father)"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y25
    yuki"I worry about him, you know?"
    yuki"He‚Äôs not getting any younger, and probably doing more around here than he should."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    mc"Well [s_name] and I will do what we can to take a lot of the workload off your father."
    mc"We‚Äôll hopefully be getting more staff to help us over the coming days."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    yuki"Thanks, that‚Äôs at least reassuring."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    mc"How about you? What is it that you do for a living?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    yuki"I‚Äôve dabbled in a few different things. But right now I‚Äôve been training to be a seaplane pilot."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    mc"Really? That‚Äôs an interesting choice of career. Who may I ask inspired this future path?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y27
    yuki"My father actually. He taught me everything there is to know about being a pilot."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    yuki"Back in his heyday, he was a very experienced commercial pilot, but he started his career off as a local seaplane pilot."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    mc"So I gather that you‚Äôre hoping to follow in his footsteps?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y25
    yuki"Someday, but I don‚Äôt know. I‚Äôve been spending more and more time checking on him."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y25
    yuki"I mean just last week I had to take him to see his local GP because [s_name] was having some kind of meltdown after that idiot Randy fell down a flight of stairs in the lighthouse."
    yuki"[s_name] called me to come by and take father to the doctors."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    mc"Is he okay?"
    yuki"Father said he had an unusual coughing fit, but his doctor said it was nothing to worry about."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    yuki"Anyways, I‚Äôm hoping that I can soon attain my sport pilot certificate."
    yuki"I‚Äôve logged the required twenty hours of flight time, with five of those being able to fly solo."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    yuki"But I still need to receive two hours of dual instruction in the preceding two months, pass a written test, and pass a practical test also."
    mc"Even though you haven‚Äôt got your full license yet, that‚Äôs still pretty damn impressive Yuki, especially given your age."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y27
    yuki"Age is no barrier if you want something badly enough [y_name]."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    mc"I agree. It would be great if you get your pilots license, I‚Äôm sure your Dad would be pretty proud of you."
    yuki"I hope so. But my main area of expertise is with electronics, computers more specifically."
    mc"Oh, really?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y27
    yuki"Yeah, I know it sounds pretty cliche..."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    yuki"But I‚Äôve always been good with gadgets and setting things up on the various computers that I had when I was growing up."
    yuki"I actually designed my very own virus protection program when I was fourteen."
    mc"Wow, that‚Äôs really remarkable Yuki."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    yuki"How about you? Are you an expert in the field of hotel management?"
    mc"Haha, hardly."
    mc"Before I came out here to Sunshine Bay to help [s_name], I‚Äôd been practising law as a junior associate."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y25
    yuki"Is that so?"
    mc"You seem surprised?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    yuki"I am, it‚Äôs just that I also had a serious interest in studying law right before I graduated from high school."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    mc"What stopped you?"
    yuki"Well you see [y_name], I‚Äôm an only child, and after my mother passed away, I decided to check in on my father whenever I could."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y25
    yuki"And if I wanted to study law, I would have to leave for the big city, and I didn‚Äôt think I‚Äôd be able to handle being so far away from him for so long."
    mc"That‚Äôs understandable. I kind of know how you feel."
    yuki"You lost your mother too?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    mc"Yeah, when I was five. It was a few good years before my father recovered from losing her, as did I."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y25
    yuki"It seems like we have a few things in common, for better or for worse."
    mc"Yeah it does. "
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    yuki"So how far did you get with your career in law?"
    mc"After nearly seven years of studying at law school, I‚Äôve spent the past couple of years working for a firm in my hometown just waiting for the opportunity to further my career."
    mc"I thought I was all set to be made a senior associate with the firm that I was at, that was until they-"
    # (Yuki ends his sentence)"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y25
    yuki"Hired someone else instead?"
    mc"Yeah‚Ä¶ And then they let me go as well."
    yuki"Man, that‚Äôs rough."
    mc"It‚Äôs a pretty cut-throat industry."
    mc"It‚Äôs kill or be killed most days, and even worse than that if you ever become a big name lawyer."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    mc"My partner Nicole is a senior associate with her firm you see."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    yuki"That explains how you know so much."
    yuki"So what brings you here to Sunshine Bay then, besides [s_name] inviting you?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y26
    mc"I guess I needed a change of scenery, a different challenge, something that is worlds away from my normal life and the line of work that I‚Äôd been doing for so many years."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y27
    yuki"Well you came to the right place!"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    mc"It sure feels like it. So, did you fly a seaplane to get here?"
    yuki"Oh yeah, I parked it out on the beachfront, knocked over few kids sandcastles during my landing."
    mc"You did?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y27
    yuki"No of course not you simpleton! Haha, I rode my scooter here."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y35
    yuki"Say‚Ä¶ I could take you up there if you‚Äôd like? When you have a day free that is. "
    # (Yuki points up to the sky, or out the window to show she‚Äôs pointing at the sky)"

    menu:
        "I‚Äôm keen"(wt="Best choice"):
            $ v_day2_yuki_seaplane = True
            show sc day2roshiyuki y26
            mc"Yeah I‚Äôm definitely interested for sure!"
            show sc day2roshiyuki y27
            $ yuki_points = change_stat(yuki_points,1,"Yuki")
            yuki"Great. I‚Äôm already looking forward to it." #+1 YUKI POINT"
        "Perhaps not":
            show sc day2roshiyuki y26
            mc"Oh. Hmm‚Ä¶ Perhaps not. It‚Äôs not really my thing."
            show sc day2roshiyuki y27
            yuki"What‚Äôs wrong? Are you afraid of heights [y_name]?"
            show sc day2roshiyuki y24
            mc"No it‚Äôs not that, it‚Äôs just-"


    show sc day2roshiyuki y06
    s"Hey you two. I‚Äôm not interrupting anything, am I?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y28
    jump lb_day2_mr_roshi_meeting_3

label lb_day2_mr_roshi_meeting_3:
    yuki"Nope, just having a nice friendly chat with [y_name]."

label lb_day2_mr_roshi_meeting_4:
    show sc day2roshiyuki y10
    s"I hope he was behaving himself?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
    yuki"Haha yeah, he was the perfect gentlemen."
    mc"Thanks, I guess."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y29
    yuki"How‚Äôs my father doing?"
    show sc day2roshiyuki y12
    s"Well he fell asleep pretty quickly after his head hit the pillow."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y11
    s"Your Dad has been working himself way too hard of late, ever since I told him about the situation with the hotel."
    s"I mean I appreciate everything he‚Äôs doing, but his health is more important right now."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y30
    yuki"I agree. And look, don‚Äôt sweat it [s_name]."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y31
    yuki"Whatever my father can‚Äôt do, then I‚Äôll fill in and help you out in any way that I can."
    show sc day2roshiyuki y24
