label lb_day2_eve_s:
    # (MOW) 05 - MC and F call it a day for work. they sit on the hill, looking at the ocean, talking, drinking beer"
    # - The MC is talking to his Best Friend"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (MC and F finish up in the last hotel room, put back together, looks brand-new)"
    # (F has her hands to the back of her head, eyes, open she looks exhausted - https://previews.123rf.com/images/leonardophoto/leonardophoto1906/leonardophoto190600054/124137673-tired-excited-young-blonde-woman-touching-her-head-by-both-hands-standing-with-closed-eyes-on-light-.jpg)"
    scene sc day2eves s01
    with dissolve
    s"There, all done. For today at least."
    show sc day2eves s02
    mc"I think we made some real progress [s_name], with help from Mister Roshi and Yuki."
    show sc day2eves s03
    s"Yeah exactly. Imagine what we could do with even more sets of hands helping us out?"
    show sc day2eves s02
    mc"There‚Äôs no reason why we can‚Äôt make that a possibility real soon."
    show sc day2eves s04
    s"So, I‚Äôm gonna go to the bathroom, and when I come back, would you like to have a drink with me somewhere outside, overlooking the ocean perhaps?"
    mc"That sounds really nice actually. Where are we going exactly?"
    show sc day2eves s03
    s"You‚Äôll know when you see it. I‚Äôll meet you out front in about fifteen minutes, okay?"
    show sc day2eves s04
    mc"Sure thing [s_name]."
    # (F leaves the room)"
    show sc day2eves s22
    mc"(Now this is much better. We‚Äôre not fighting, and there doesn‚Äôt seem to be any reason why we would start an argument.)"
    mc"(When [s_name] is like this, I could easily spend several hours in her company.)"
    show sc day2eves s23
    mc"(But there‚Äôs always going to be the fear that something will cause a disagreement between us‚Ä¶)"
    mc"(It would actually be a relief if we could go a whole day without that happening‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (MC and friend walk along a path near the beach, friend carries a small basket that has some beers and snacks in them)"



label lb_day2_eve_s_sunset:
    if _in_replay:
        if y_name == None:
            $ y_name = "MC"
        else:
            $ y_name = persistent.y_name

        if s_name == None:
            $ s_name = "S"
        else:
            $ s_name = persistent.s_name

        show screen toprightmenu

        play music "music/01/2936-fliegen-by-sascha-ende.mp3"
    scene sc day2eves s06
    with dissolve
    mc"So where is this place [s_name]?"
    show sc day2eves s05
    s"Right up there, on the hill."
    show sc day2eves s07
    s"Come with me."
    # (F grabs his hand and walks up the hill, as the MC follows her from behind - getting a great view)"
    # (First shot could look like this with her looking back at him - https://pixhost.to/show/384/134486369_8b0a7a1324232341.jpg)"
    # (And then a full shot of him being pulled up the hill with her)"
    # (MC and F get up the hill and he sees an awesome view of the ocean, maybe the town and the lighthouse as well, depending on the angle you use)"
    # e.g. https://jonnymelon.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/burleigh-hill-4070161-e1523430392897.jpg"
    # https://fscomps.fotosearch.com/compc/OJO/OJO257/senior-couple-with-picnic-basket-on-stock-photo__pe0072589.jpg"
    # https://cdn3.eyeem.com/thumb/dbe4d59fbd6617b1c8a8bb735820b312b6a6daa8-1527804588749/w/1280"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Beach_Ocean_Waves_-_Sound_Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    scene sc day2eves s08
    with dissolve
    mc"Wow‚Ä¶"
    s"What did I tell you? Pretty awesome, huh?"
    mc"This is amazing [s_name]."
    # (F sits down on the picnic mat with two drinks in hand and the picnic basket open showing some food)"
    show sc day2eves s10
    s"Sit with me [y_name], and let‚Äôs have that drink together."
    show sc day2eves s09
    mc"Okay."
    # (The MC sits on the picnic mat next to F.)"
    # (Alternate the shots her MD - a shot of the MC and friend sitting on the same matt, a behind shot so we see the ocean in the background, and closeups)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc day2eves s11
    with dissolve
    s"So, quite a day, huh?"
    # (both of them hold a drink in their hand as they talk)"
    show sc day2eves s13
    mc"Yeah, it was. It‚Äôs amazing what can be achieved in ten or twelve hours."
    mc"But time seems to get away from you the longer you work."
    show sc day2eves s15
    s"I know what you mean. So much to do, so very little time."
    show sc day2eves s13
    s"[y_name], can I ask you something?"
    mc"You know that you can [s_name]."
    s"Where do you see yourself in five years, or even ten years?"
    s"I mean, has your future plans changed much due to what has happened this past week?"
    s"You know, with your job and then coming down here for the summer?"
    mc"Hmm‚Ä¶ Interesting question. I haven‚Äôt thought about it too much to be honest."
    mc"I guess if you were to have asked me that question a couple of weeks ago..."
    mc"Then I would‚Äôve told you in five years time, I would be hoping to be a full-time public interest lawyer by then."
    mc"Or if I were to set my goals even higher, a trial lawyer for criminal law."
    show sc day2eves s15
    s"That sounds like a huge goal to aim for!"
    mc"Yeah it sure is."
    show sc day2eves s13
    mc"I also pictured that one day, Nicole and I would both be highly successful lawyers, we‚Äôd own a big house, we‚Äôd eventually get married and have a few kids before we hit our mid-thirties."
    s"Wow, you have it all mapped out by the sound of things."
    mc"Maybe, maybe not."
    mc"I‚Äôm finding that every time I feel like I'm on the right path to having all of those things, I get knocked off it and I‚Äôm drifting further away from those goals."
    show sc day2eves s12
    s"Well, maybe you shouldn‚Äôt see it as drifting away, but instead, you‚Äôre simply taking a different route, albeit a longer one."
    mc"I suppose so."
    show sc day2eves s13
    mc"What about you?"
    mc"Do you want the fairytale life, a big house, a rich and successful husband, and a couple of rug rats?"
    show sc day2eves s15
    jump lb_day2_eve_s_sunset_1

label lb_day2_eve_s_sunset_1:
    s"Nah, I already had a glimpse of what that would be like when we lived with my Mom and Gerald."

label lb_day2_eve_s_sunset_2:
