            show sc day2eves s18
            mc"I know how to self-motivate myself even in the worst of times. It‚Äôs what I‚Äôm good at."
            mc"I try and see everything as an opportunity rather than a problem, like your hotel situation for instance. "
            mc"We both just need to be willing to take action and work together for the combined goal that we want."
            show sc day2eves s20
            s"You have so much confidence about you [y_name]. Do you mind if I borrow a lot of it sometime?"
            show sc day2eves s17
            mc"Haha, it‚Äôs all yours whenever you want it."
        "Don't do it":
            show sc day2eves s13
            mc"Hey, it‚Äôs okay."
            mc"The hotel will be fine. YOU, will be fine."
            mc"We‚Äôve made some great progress these past couple of days."
            mc"And like you said, imagine what we could do over the course of a full week?"
            # (F smiles)"
            show sc day2eves s12
            s"Mmm‚Ä¶ Thanks [y_name]."
            s"That‚Äôs what I think I‚Äôve needed these past few weeks, a positive influence."
            show sc day2eves s14
            s"Someone to be the optimist while I‚Äôm so pessimistic about things."
            show sc day2eves s12
            mc"Haha, being optimistic is something that is automatically instilled in my mindset."
            show sc day2eves s13
            mc"I needed to constantly think like that to get through my course and to attain my law degree."
            mc"I know how to self-motivate myself even in the worst of times. It‚Äôs what I‚Äôm good at."
            mc"I try and see everything as an opportunity rather than a problem, like your hotel situation for instance. "
