    ash"Look behind you..."
    show sc opening129
    with vpunch
    lt"Oh! Now I see what you mean by ‚Äúwe‚Äù."
    show sc opening125
    ash"This is my daughter, she just turned nine."
    ash"My neighbour usually looks after her for me while I‚Äôm at work."
    ash"She just dropped her off when I messaged her to say I was on my way home."
    ash"She‚Äôs a nice old lady who has been like a grandma to her."
