    show sc opening132
    lt"That‚Äôs kids though for you Ashley."
    show sc opening131
    lt"They have such big imaginations, and at that age, they don‚Äôt fear much, and they believe anything is possible."
    show sc opening130
    lt"It sounds like your daughter is the positive voice that you need to hear from time to time."
    show sc opening134
    ash"Yeah, you‚Äôre right."
    show sc opening131
    lt"If you don‚Äôt mind me asking you Ashley, but what happened with [s_name]‚Äôs father?"
    show sc opening137
    ash"You know what, I have no idea. And I‚Äôd prefer to keep it that way."
    show sc opening132
    lt"How come?"
    show sc opening135
