    show sc opening140
    lt"I haven‚Äôt stopped thinking about you since last night."
    show sc opening142
    lt"And when I saw you up on that stage, and you looked at me the same way, I know you felt the same, didn‚Äôt you?"
    # (Ash tries to look away but can‚Äôt)"
    show sc opening145
    ash"I um‚Ä¶ Yeah I did."
    show sc opening140
    lt"You know, there‚Äôs obviously a reason why our paths have crossed."
    lt"To me, it can‚Äôt be a coincidence that my ship had to dock here in Sunshine Bay."
    lt"And of all the clubs that I had to walk into, it had to be the one I found you in. I believe in fate, and-"
